name: NFT generator clicker!
description:
Hi! this is first version of game clicker and an NFT generator, you click on the button and a random NFT is generated from the accessories available to you, accessories affect the price of NFT and you can sell NFT and improve the button to get more NFT, or buy a capsule with accessories to open new accessories, if people like this game, then I will I will develop it, I made it by the way on a YouTube video if you can and want to support me, then you can do it here:
